I bought one for my VW Thing off of ebay for 10$ because it said bus/bug on
the description and not Thing and i know it fits a 68-71 bus but not sure
about the single cabs.  it is polished aluminum on the outside part that
spins and is a stock part.  Most all the VW thing dealers, thing shop,
things unlimited, etc, sell them new but they are not cheap.

